<B> What is the Tiny Chao garden?</B></FONT></TD>
<TR> 
<TD BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" VALIGN="CENTER"><A NAME="7"><FONT SIZE="2">
What is the Tiny Chao garden?<BR>
Can I go there without "Sonic Advance"?</FONT></A></TD>
</TABLE>
<TABLE BORDER=0 WIDTH=100% CELLSPACING=0 CELLPADDING=3>
<TR> 
<TD VALIGN="bottom" HEIGHT=16 BGCOLOR="#FFCC00"><IMG SRC="../chao_images/a.gif"></TD>
<TR> 
<TD BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" VALIGN="CENTER"> 
<FONT SIZE="2"> 
The Tiny Chao garden refers to the little garden found in the Game Boy Advance.<BR>
In the Tiny Chao garden, there are 2 mini-games to earn rings and buy fruits to raise your Chao.<BR>
There are also special eggs that can only be bought in the Tiny Chao garden...something a Chao breeder would not want to miss!</FONT> 
</TD>
