<B>How do I get more Chao?</B></FONT></TD>
<TR> 
<TD BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" VALIGN="CENTER"><A NAME="8"><FONT SIZE="2">
I only have 2 Chao in my garden...<BR>
How do I get more?</FONT></A></TD>
</TABLE>
<TABLE BORDER="0" WIDTH=100% CELLSPACING="0" CELLPADDING="3">
