<TD BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" VALIGN="CENTER"><FONT SIZE="2">
When Chao grow up and are ready to matea flower will bloom around them.
Once this Chao is ready, you must find another Chao ready to mate.
They will perform a short dance, after which an egg will be created.
This is how Chao are born.
In the case you want to increase the chance of your Chao to mate, feed them "Heart" fruits.
</FONT></TD>
